Parser code lacks XML documentation comments, making it harder for contributors to understand complex GFF parsing logic.

**Scope**:
- ArcLightDialogParser.cs  
- GffBinaryReader.cs
- GffParser.cs base class
- Complex field index mapping methods
- List writing methods

**Impact**: Makes onboarding contributors harder - complex Aurora format logic not self-documented

**Solution**: Add XML documentation comments with summary, params, and returns tags

**Example**:
```csharp
/// <summary>
/// Calculates the actual field indices count based on 4:1 Aurora pattern
/// </summary>
/// <param name="allFields">List of all GFF fields</param>
/// <returns>Field count (not byte count - caller multiplies by 4)</returns>
private uint CalculateActualFieldIndicesCount(List<GffField> allFields)
```

**Note**: High-level architecture is documented in PARSER_ARCHITECTURE.md. This issue is about inline XML comments for IntelliSense and code-level documentation.

**Source**: TECHDEBT.md - API Documentation

## Description

Design and implement core plugin APIs that plugins can access. Includes audio service (LibVLCSharp), UI command service, file dialog service, and event notification system.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Audio service API (playback, recording via LibVLCSharp)
- [ ] UI command service API (create panels, show dialogs)
- [ ] File dialog service API (sandboxed file access)
- [ ] Event notification system (dialog changes, node selection, etc.)
- [ ] Permission enforcement at API boundaries
- [ ] API documentation for plugin developers

## Technical Notes

**Audio Service** (via LibVLCSharp):
```csharp
public interface IAudioService
{
    Task PlayAudio(string filePath);
    Task<byte[]> RecordAudio(TimeSpan duration);
    Task<WaveformData> GenerateWaveform(string filePath);
}
```

**UI Command Service**:
```csharp
public interface IUIService
{
    void CreatePanel(string title, object content);
    Task<bool> ShowDialog(string message, string title);
    void ShowNotification(string message);
}
```

**File Dialog Service** (sandboxed):
```csharp
public interface IFileService
{
    Task<string?> OpenFileDialog(string filter);
    Task<string?> SaveFileDialog(string filter);
    Task<byte[]> ReadFile(string path); // Permission checked
}
```

**Event Notification**:
```csharp
public interface IEventService
{
    IObservable<DialogChangedEvent> DialogChanged { get; }
    IObservable<NodeSelectedEvent> NodeSelected { get; }
}
```

**Permission Enforcement**:
- Check manifest permissions before API calls
- Throw `PermissionDeniedException` if unauthorized
- Log permission violations

## Dependencies

**Part of**: Epic 0 - Plugin Foundation (#37)  
**Blocks**: Python bootstrap library (#48)  
**Requires**: Process isolation infrastructure (#45), Plugin manifest system (#46)

## Estimated Effort

L (5-7 days)

---

**Related Documentation**: LibVLCSharp, gRPC service definitions, permission models
